title: Is This Beto O’Rourke with the Words ‘Feminist’ and ‘Vegan’ Painted on His Body?
subtitle: Photographs from a Pride parades have not uncommonly been re-purposed for political reasons.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: A photograph shows Beto O'Rourke with words such as "feminist," "vegan," "atheist," and "queer" painted on his body.
